{"word":"θάνατος","slug":"θάνατος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϑάνατος, ου, ὁ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:θανατόω\">θανατόω</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:θνῄσκω\">θνῄσκω</a></el>] <b>death<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in the natural physical sense <b><a href='B:470 10:21'>Mt 10:21</a>; <a href='B:480 7:10'>Mk 7:10</a>; <a href='B:490 2:26'>Lk 2:26</a>; <a href='B:500 11:4'>J 11:4</a>, <a href='B:500 11:13'>13</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a>; owing to a specific cause <b><a href='B:730 2:23'>Rv 2:23</a>; <a href='B:730 6:8'>6:8b</a>; <a href='B:730 18:8'>18:8</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in extended sense, of existence viewed outside a relationship with God <b><a href='B:470 4:16'>Mt 4:16</a>; <a href='B:500 8:51'>J 8:51</a>; <a href='B:520 7:24'>Ro 7:24</a>; <a href='B:540 3:7'>2 Cor 3:7</a>; <a href='B:660 1:15'>Js 1:15</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> = eternal death <b><a href='B:520 1:32'>Ro 1:32</a>; <a href='B:520 7:5'>7:5</a>; <a href='B:540 7:10'>2 Cor 7:10</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:θανατηφόρος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:θανατόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}